### 角色列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取角色详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "运营经理",
  "code": "ops_manager",
  "description": "负责门店日常运营管理"
}

### 更新角色
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "高级运营经理",
  "description": "负责多门店运营管理"
}

### 删除角色
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取角色的菜单权限
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/1/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 给角色分配菜单
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/1/menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menu_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}
